## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d4c36-587">值為 0 表示沒有限制 （嘗試執行命令會無限期等候）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4c36-587">A value of 0 indicates no limit (an attempt to execute a command will wait indefinitely).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="d4c36-588"><xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.CommandTimeout%2A>屬性將會忽略在非同步方法呼叫期間例如<xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.BeginExecuteReader%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4c36-588">The <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.CommandTimeout%2A> property will be ignored during asynchronous method calls such as <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.BeginExecuteReader%2A>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d4c36-589"><xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.CommandTimeout%2A> 沒有任何作用，針對內容連接執行命令 (<xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection>以開啟 「 內容連線 = true"的連接字串中)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4c36-589"><xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlCommand.CommandTimeout%2A> has no effect when the command is executed against a context connection (a <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlConnection> opened with "context connection=true" in the connection string).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="d4c36-590">在命令執行或的結果處理期間，這個屬性會是累計的逾時 （適用於所有網路封包讀取方法引動過程） 對所有網路讀取。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4c36-590">This property is the cumulative time-out (for all network packets that are read during the invocation of a method) for all network reads during command execution or processing of the results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d4c36-591">第一個資料列會傳回，而且不包含使用者的處理時間之後，仍然會發生逾時，只有網路讀取時間。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4c36-591">A time-out can still occur after the first row is returned, and does not include user processing time, only network read time.</span></span>  
>   
>  <span data-ttu-id="d4c36-592">例如，使用 30 秒鐘的時間時，如果<xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDataReader.Read%2A>需要兩個網路封包，則讀取兩者的網路封包的情況下，它在必須 30 秒。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4c36-592">For example, with a 30 second time out, if <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDataReader.Read%2A> requires two network packets, then it has 30 seconds to read both network packets.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d4c36-593">如果您呼叫<xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDataReader.Read%2A>同樣地，它會有另一個的 30 秒，以讀取它需要的任何資料。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4c36-593">If you call <xref:System.Data.SqlClient.SqlDataReader.Read%2A> again, it will have another 30 seconds to read any data that it requires.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System;  
using System.Data.SqlClient;  
///   
public class A {  
   ///   
   public static void Main() {  
      string connectionString = "";  
      // Wait for 5 second delay in the command  
      string queryString = "waitfor delay '00:00:05'";  
      using (SqlConnection connection = new SqlConnection(connectionString)) {  
         connection.Open();  
         SqlCommand command = new SqlCommand(queryString, connection);  
         // Setting command timeout to 1 second  
         command.CommandTimeout = 1;  
         try {  
            command.ExecuteNonQuery();  
         }  
         catch (SqlException e) {  
            Console.WriteLine("Got expected SqlException due to command timeout ");  
            Console.WriteLine(e);  
         }  
      }  
   }  
}  
```
